description:
        This package wraps up the process of fetching exchange rates from
        OpenExchangeRates.org.  You will need an AppID.

library
        exposed-modules:
                Currency.OpenExchangeRates

        build-depends:
                base == 4.*,
                containers,
                currency,
                text,
                aeson >= 0.6.1.0,
